yTime":"2016-12-20T16:00:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>掉佢落海啦 仲幫佢搵老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算𠴱陣知道佢係蝗仔都唔忍心掉佢落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa3eb64add416f55c02b8be0e33be62a766f5e1","tid":47813,"uid":10214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T16:01:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日記嚟㗎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都算係"},{"pid":"7da67761ed34929577cd29880cb5e72145ce5aa8","tid":47813,"uid":10214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T16:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>知己知己<br />\n唔知點解放埋落一大段野果度就好唔順口</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我好撚順口喎"},{"pid":"1d13ef132eea7f546161f58d4b6b277f5ecd34cf","tid":47813,"uid":10214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T16:02:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩隻手放左喺槍袋上面<br />\n睇到呢句笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n完全唔了解點解個傻鳩要咁做"},{"pid":"2166102f3cfd907ac3dc7f36288bd24a871aef9f","tid":47813,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T16:04:11.000Z","msg":"仙子你個海旁唔係得個啊婆既咩 今日咁熱鬧既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}